(click:?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[As you flip through the pages of the worn book, your fingers tracing the faded words and illustrations, you reach the end. Curiosity compels you to glance at the final pages, and there, tucked away near the back, you notice something intriguing. Amongst the final paragraphs and notes, a small handwritten number catches your eye: a number 7.]

(click:?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[It seems inconspicuous at first, a mere digit on the page, but a spark of recognition ignites within you. Could this number hold significance?

