:: examine box {"position":"350,1200","size":"100,100"}
|unlocked)[(t8n:"fade-right")[Your gaze falls upon a small, hidden compartment tucked away within the closet. It's appearance feels familiar to you. With a gasp, you remember where you've seen the same hidden compartment before.]

(click: ?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[You were always a curious toddler, and once, you were playing hide and seek with the other shrine children. You hid underneath the bed, certain that none of the other children would check there.]

(click: ?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[As you were waiting to be found, your grandfather came running in, carrying something in his hands and muttering about needing more strength. You remember seeing him open this same closet and crouch down, placing that item in his hands in the closet.]

(click: ?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[Later that evening, you remember the shrine becoming agitated over a lost artifact, but you can't quite remember what it was.]

(click: ?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[Intrigued by what your grandfather could have hid, you carefully open the compartment, and there, nestled among moth-bitten blankets and pillows, you discover a ceremonial plate. Its intricate design reflects the craftsmanship of the artisans who once served the shrine, crafting items of reverence and devotion.]

(click: ?page)+(t8n:"fade-right")[You grasp the ceremonial plate, feeling its weight and significance in your hands. It serves as a tangible connection to the rituals and traditions upheld by your ancestors. With each item you collect, the shrine's restoration draws nearer, and the bond between past and present strengthens.(show:?back)]]\

